Company Overview of Formula XO, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Formula XO, Inc. develops, manufactures, and distributes hair care products. The company offers illumai Biome Care System to protect, nurture, and maintain the biome of the hair, skin, and scalp. It offers shampoos, conditioners, and sprays. The company sells its products through salons in California, District Of Columbia, Massachusetts, New York, Texas, and Virginia, as well as online. Formula XO, Inc. was founded in 2013 and is based in Sterling, Virginia


46400 Benedict DriveSuite 203Sterling, VA 20164United StatesFounded in 2013



Phone: 703-888-2565

