Formula Xo, Inc. Illumai Nurture ConditionerBy FORMULA XO, INC.Product Details
    Strengthen your hair with Nurture, a silicone-free conditioner that reinforces all hair types with patented Isoleucine. Restore your damaged areas and stimulate the self-healing properties of your biome for stronger, shinier and more manageable hair with natural lift and healthy movement. 3 minutes on, All Day Strong! Nurture is made of naturally derived ingredients and is PETA certified. It contains no sulfates, no silicones, no preservatives, no parabens and is gluten free, GMO free, and nut free. It is safe for all hair types and is especially effective in detoxing and nurturing chemically and color-treated hair. Nurture is part of the scientifically integrated Illumai biome care system. Mixing and matching with other shampoos and conditioners won't have the same healthy beauty benefits!





