Formula Xo, Inc. Illumai Cleanse ShampooBy FORMULA XO, INC.Product Details
    A sulfate-free lather that feels good and is good for you, Cleanse is made of naturally derived ingredients and is PETA certified. It contains no sulfates, no silicones, no preservatives, no parabens and is gluten free, GMO free, and nut free. It is safe for all hair types and is especially effective in detoxing and nurturing chemically and color-treated hair. Cleanse is part of the scientifically integrated Illumai biome care system. Mixing and matching with other shampoos and conditioners won't have the same healthy beauty benefits! too. Made with naturally derived XO-70®, Cleanse lifts dirt and excess oil but leaves essential proteins, peptides and lipids intact, restoring your biome's balance. Hair stays cleaner, feels fuller and more moisturized, looks vibrant and dries faster. No harsh chemicals, no color fade and no frizz!





