Company







Overview



Overview








There was a problem loading your content.



Product






















Video










The illumai Essential System is a three-step hair cleansing system that delivers truly remarkable results owing to a patented, revolutionary new approach invented by Michael Zasloff, MD, PhD (former head of genetics research at NIH and dean of research at Georgetown Medical School) and refined by Mario Russo (a multi-year winner of Elle's "Top 100" list of hair stylists).The… · More illumai system is the first and only "biome care system" for the hair.  The biome is the the living ecosystem of scalp, follicles, hair, glands, peptides, proteins, moisturizing oils, and related microbiota that keep your scalp and hair heathy and well-functioning.  Conventional shampoos and conditioners damage the biome by stripping the protective lipids from your head and replacing them with man-made silicones and other lubricants.  The illumai Essential System does not do this ... and the results are not only much healthier, but hair is shiny, soft, manageable, stronger and more natural.





Launches








0










Illumai Essential System


January 2015—A 3-part, clean formula system that delivers fabulous hair 


The illumai Essential System* is a 3-step plan for healthy, beautiful hair. It’s simple: each part of the system cultivates your biome – nature’s… · More brilliant design for healthy beauty. They work together to keep your hair and scalp healthy and protected. Get manageable, shiny, frizz-free hair that’s full of healthy beauty, instead of damaged hair with artificial coatings. Join the fans of healthy beauty and reveal your true brilliance.







By
Wayne Willis
















